Class ColorProfile

  • java.lang.Object
    • view.ColorProfile

  • public class ColorProfile
extends java.lang.Object
    Color profile for the GameBoard. Allows you to set and get the cell- and grid-colors. You can also set weather or not the grid should be drawn.
